<L>__{interior car morning}
<A>__{quoyle driving alone in his best suit. which is also his worst suit. which is also the suit he wore to interview ed punch, years ago. hard rain. potholes. around a curve, to see ahead... rear angle of a tall woman, holding the hand of a child as they walk in their slickers through the downpour. as he passes them, they turn and.. ...the woman is petal. the child is bunny. they both stick their tongues out at him. past now. looking in the rear view. the woman is lovely and no longer petal. the child is a boy, with a slack face and warm smile. surprisingly, the same mother and son that bunny watched on the ferry.}
